OL,3,CDevon & Cornwall Police unveil plan to
OL,4,Cbolster frontline presence in
OL,5,Ccommunities
OL,7,FMore than 120 police officers are set
OL,8,Fto join frontline patrols across Devon
OL,9,Fand Cornwall as part of a significant
OL,10,Fpush to strengthen community policing
OL,11,Fin the region.
OL,13,FThe initiative, unveiled by Chief
OL,14,FConstable James Vaughan to the Police
OL,15,Fand Crime Panel in Plymouth, will see
OL,16,F71 officers integrated into existing
OL,17,Fpatrol teams by the end of 2025, with
OL,18,Fa further 50 following by the end of
OL,19,FMarch 2026.
