OL,3,CDevon & Cornwall Police unveil plan to
OL,4,Cbolster frontline presence in
OL,5,Ccommunities
OL,7,FThe boost in frontline numbers is
OL,8,Fbeing delivered through a combination
OL,9,Fof measures: redeploying experienced
OL,10,Fofficers from other roles, recruiting
OL,11,Ffrom neighbouring forces, and bringing
OL,12,Fin new constables through fresh
OL,13,Frecruitment drives.
OL,15,FBeyond the patrol teams, the force is
OL,16,Falso investing in neighbourhood
OL,17,Fpolicing, with 50 officers moving into
OL,18,Fdedicated community roles and
OL,19,Frecruitment is under way for 50
OL,20,Fadditional police community support
OL,21,Fofficers.
