OL,7,FChief Constable James Vaughan
OL,8,Facknowledged that achieving this
OL,9,Frestructure had required difficult
OL,10,Fdecisions but emphasised the
OL,11,Fimportance of building resilience
OL,12,Facross the organisation.
OL,14,FHe said, "Since taking up the role of
OL,15,FChief Constable, strengthening our
OL,16,Ffrontline capacity has been a priority.
