OL,3,CDevon & Cornwall Police unveil plan to
OL,4,Cbolster frontline presence in
OL,5,Ccommunities
OL,7,F"The changes we've made haven't always
OL,8,Fbeen easy, but they've been necessary.
OL,9,FNow we need to maintain this momentum
OL,10,Fand ensure our resources are
OL,11,Fpositioned effectively for the long
OL,12,Fterm".
OL,14,FThe force is actively encouraging
OL,15,Fpeople interested in policing careers
OL,16,Fto come forward.
OL,18,F"We're looking for people who want to
OL,19,Fhelp keep our communities safe", Chief
OL,20,FConstable Vaughan added.
