OL,3,CDevon & Cornwall Police unveil plan to
OL,4,Cbolster frontline presence in
OL,5,Ccommunities
OL,7,FPolice and Crime Commissioner Alison
OL,8,FHernandez expressed her support for
OL,9,Fthe move, which responds directly to
OL,10,Fpublic demand for greater police
OL,11,Fvisibility on local streets.
OL,13,FShe said, "Communities across Devon
OL,14,Fand Cornwall have consistently told me
OL,15,Fthey want to see more officers out and
OL,16,Fabout in their neighbourhoods.
OL,18,F"It helps people feel safer and acts
OL,19,Fas a genuine deterrent to criminal
OL,20,Factivity. I'm pleased to see these
OL,21,Fplans now taking shape".
